{"tid":2343108,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"深入淺出–延壽藥物的研究(一)","createTime":"2020-12-27T16:06:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-28T08:38:50.000Z","uid":38861,"like":26,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"09df7a7db45ee34a9b812e31b96a5ecc3e80be01","tid":2343108,"uid":38861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T16:06:58.000Z","msg":"往不同動物例如老鼠及線蟲注射治療糖尿病的藥物(Metformin)後，壽命均會有顯著的增長。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MC9qMKq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMC9qMKq.jpg&h=42efcf75&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有研究利用現成資料庫作對比，發現服用Metformin的<span class=\"blue\">糖尿病人</span>歲數比沒有服用Metformin的<span class=\"red\">健康人士</span>為長(Ref1)，亦有臨床研究嘗試為14名70歲的健康老人家注射為期6星期的Metformin，藉觀察體內的轉變以作抗衰老藥的研究基礎(Ref2)。<br />\n<br />\n（圖2）從圖中可見，往年輕線蟲注射Metformin的話，牠們的生存日子便會增長。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NWRD6KD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNWRD6KD.png&h=f4d422d2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n（圖3）但是，與年輕線蟲相反，往年老的線蟲注射Metformin的話，牠們的生存日子不但沒有增加，反而會減少。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2PZBTpG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2PZBTpG.png&h=507d37fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n（圖4）經過一系列的實驗，科學家認為Metformin能夠驅使年輕線蟲延壽的其中一個原因，是與粒線體的整體功用有關(Ref3)。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WFoGj4L.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWFoGj4L.png&h=1912be3d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n其中，Metformin為年輕線蟲的新陳代謝作出轉變，包括增加碳水化合物的分解，減低脂肪的含量等，但年老的線蟲卻沒能夠觸發同樣的效果，反而更會因新陳代謝機制的不良負荷而增加死亡率。<br />\n<br />\n文中的科學家亦就此作出質疑，既然Metformin只能使年輕線蟲而非年老線蟲延壽，那又究竟是否值得「魯莽」地對健康老人家進行Metformin的延壽研究。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"teal\">如果想我快啲出文的話，請入去Penana網站科普專欄&ndash;薯不揀單俾一個like以及Bookmark，這對我非常之重要。</span><br />\n<br />\nLink: <a href=\"https://www.penana.com/story/66244/%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84-%E8%96%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%8F%80%E5%96%AE/toc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Fstory%2F66244%2F%25E7%25A7%2591%25E6%2599%25AE%25E5%25B0%2588%25E6%25AC%2584-%25E8%2596%25AF%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%258F%2580%25E5%2596%25AE%2Ftoc&d=%2BrTTj2V4oNsvrkryR3gjd92ufVLooqfEZhiAoxVhWLg%3D&h=06723ead\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/story/66244/%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84-%E8%96%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%8F%80%E5%96%AE/toc</a><br />\n<br />\n同時亦可以在Penana網站裡按「<span class=\"orange\">買一嚿/半嚿薯仔</span>」，以課金的方式推動我繼續搜羅資料寫文，多謝。<br />\n<br />\nLink:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.penana.com/user/27349/%E8%96%AF%E4%BB%94%E8%81%9E%E8%8C%B1%E8%8E%89/portfolio\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Fuser%2F27349%2F%25E8%2596%25AF%25E4%25BB%2594%25E8%2581%259E%25E8%258C%25B1%25E8%258E%2589%2Fportfolio&d=%2BrTTj2V4oNsvrkryR3gjd92ufVLooqfEZhiAoxVhWLg%3D&h=42767fd4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/user/27349/%E8%96%AF%E4%BB%94%E8%81%9E%E8%8C%B1%E8%8E%89/portfolio</a><br />\n<br />\n有興趣接收科學資訊的話，歡迎follow IG: potatopigtongue。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/potatopigtongue/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fpotatopigtongue%2F&d=%2BrTTj2V4oNsvrkryR3gjd92ufVLooqfEZhiAoxVhWLg%3D&h=a03d31fa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/potatopigtongue/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nRef1:<a href=\"https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/25041462/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2F25041462%2F&d=%2BrTTj2V4oNsvrkryR3gjd92ufVLooqfEZhiAoxVhWLg%3D&h=67fc47a4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/25041462/</a><br />\nRef2:<a href=\"https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/29383869/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2F29383869%2F&d=%2BrTTj2V4oNsvrkryR3gjd92ufVLooqfEZhiAoxVhWLg%3D&h=44452459\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/29383869/</a><br />\nRef3:<a href=\"https://www.nature.com/articles/s42255-020-00307-1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nature.com%2Farticles%2Fs42255-020-00307-1&d=%2BrTTj2V4oNsvrkryR3gjd92ufVLooqfEZhiAoxVhWLg%3D&h=dd7ac43c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.nature.com/articles/s42255-020-00307-1</a>"},{"pid":"3019d0dbffd2e13bbd171250303009bf2578318a","tid":2343108,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T16:08:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b85fc0151e0180e9d11a8094efabedcd47547fbc","tid":2343108,"uid":290895,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T16:08:15.000Z","msg":"即係點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee2471a1441a2a1f66bc56927d3e98f7feab17d4","tid":2343108,"uid":205339,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T16:08:38.000Z","msg":"仲延？<br />\n唔好延啦 好多垃圾"},{"pid":"f01c1c0a30c080bd235056ab4f8c997fd3d8d6d9","tid":2343108,"uid":236977,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T16:09:50.000Z","msg":"點睇NAD+"},{"pid":"e4ff6a3c41218d939f869a9cc33376c2af2e8a5c","tid":2343108,"uid":38861,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b85fc0151e0180e9d11a8094efabedcd47547fbc","tid":2343108,"uid":290895,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T16:08:15.000Z","msg":"即係點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T16:10:38.000Z","msg":"即係有證據指出Metformin未必可以對老人家有延壽的效用。"},{"pid":"77987d0276be9aa81b97a97b1902599b9dc3703a","tid":2343108,"uid":38861,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f01c1c0a30c080bd235056ab4f8c997fd3d8d6d9","tid":2343108,"uid":236977,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T16:09:50.000Z","msg":"點睇NAD+"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T16:10:51.000Z","msg":"下集講<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bef6d28457